               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the second half of the year (fols. 7ra-178rc)&#xD;
I-1) Maggābit (fols. 7ra-35vc)&#xD;
I-2) Miyāzyā (fols. 36ra-57rc)&#xD;
I-3) Gǝnbot (fols. 57va-83rb) &#xD;
I-4) Sane (fols. 84ra-109vc) &#xD;
I-5) Ḥamle (fols. 110ra-148rc) &#xD;
I-6) Naḥāse” (fols. 148va – 173rc) &#xD;
I-7) Ṗagʷǝmen (fols. 173va – 178rc)&#xD;
The commemorative notices are followed by a ʿarke-hymns&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
